{"title":"2.10 为什么AI产品设计越来越人性化","slug":"hrl7fo38ug9gmvqy","summary":"图片由作者创作 我经常使用 Perplexity 阅读新闻，所以当我看到它的 AI 原生浏览器 Comet 免费向公众发布时，我感到非常兴奋。 当我参观演示场地时，有什么东西吸引了我的注意。 是设计语言，是品牌形象。感觉……很诗意。 感觉就像人类在探索宇宙——不是冷冰冰、机械的科","category":"2. AI-UX体验模式","tags":["PART4️⃣ AI驱动的体验设计方法&模式","2. AI-UX体验模式"],"featured":false,"order":66,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-11-03","wordCount":3138,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/hrl7fo38ug9gmvqy","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u09c3be0d\" id=\"u09c3be0d\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176678594-d3075958-fbca-461d-96ee-a09d5482e1ae.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua634a563-9fca-4dae-8efc-2a39bb14f26%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A406%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A1904690%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A811%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22WARM%20%2FEMPATHETIC%20TECH-CENTRIC%20HUMAN-CENTRIC%20COLD%2FRATIONAL%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A546%2C%22y%22%3A114%2C%22width%22%3A257%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22WARM%20%2FEMPATHETIC%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A149%2C%22y%22%3A402%2C%22width%22%3A171%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22TECH-CENTRIC%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1024%2C%22y%22%3A403%2C%22width%22%3A200%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22HUMAN-CENTRIC%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A577%2C%22y%22%3A679%2C%22width%22%3A199%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22COLD%2FRATIONAL%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f2ece1%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue0926b7c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf425b80f\" id=\"uf425b80f\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u99fbcb98\" id=\"u99fbcb98\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片由作者创作</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u46226bd4\" id=\"u46226bd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8f5e769e\" id=\"u8f5e769e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我经常使用 Perplexity 阅读新闻，所以当我看到它的 AI 原生浏览器 Comet 免费向公众发布时，我感到非常兴奋。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u564ee2cb\" id=\"u564ee2cb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u53ba0e7f\" id=\"u53ba0e7f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">当我参观演示场地时，有什么东西吸引了我的注意。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucd540bc1\" id=\"ucd540bc1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">是设计语言，是品牌形象。感觉……很诗意。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7cfa62ac\" id=\"u7cfa62ac\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8f53b4a3\" id=\"u8f53b4a3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">感觉就像人类在探索宇宙——不是冷冰冰、机械的科技之旅，而是一种近乎诗意的体验。仿佛我们像昔日诗人漫游遥远国度那样，在太空中漂流。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufc774ffd\" id=\"ufc774ffd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u584b8091\" id=\"u584b8091\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ueefbefb8\" id=\"ueefbefb8\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176679676-39600df5-bf89-4004-b052-47034352980e.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua611200f-2150-4d6b-943a-1fe1a6b2e89%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A376%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A1663329%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A751%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22COMET%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A619%2C%22y%22%3A429%2C%22width%22%3A168%2C%22height%22%3A38%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMET%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2325465d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u437f5d9e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf752f109\" id=\"uf752f109\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f49e2d8\" id=\"u2f49e2d8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片来自迷惑彗星网站</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u628ff2cf\" id=\"u628ff2cf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5f21ab5f\" id=\"u5f21ab5f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这真的让我印象深刻。而且这也不是第一次了。多年来，我一直很喜欢克劳德的设计——那种温暖的感觉、亲切的语调，还有它充满人情味的名字。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud8add67e\" id=\"ud8add67e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4ea69f59\" id=\"u4ea69f59\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a4b2d6d\" id=\"u1a4b2d6d\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176677059-b7bc91f0-a41e-4dc5-9dd4-9406b1a54a0d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud8f28c1c-ee99-4854-9666-cb63df7f6cf%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A329%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A199452%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A657%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22MEETYOUR%20THINKING%20PARTNER%20TACKLE%20ANY%20BIG%2CBOLD%2C%20BEWILDERING%20CHALLENGE%20WITH%20CLAUDE.%20ASK%20CLAUDE%20%E4%B8%AA%20HOW%20CAN%20I%20HELP%20YOU%20TODAY%3F%20WRITE%20%2F%3E%20%20CODE%20LEARN%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A51%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A298%2C%22height%22%3A62%2C%22text%22%3A%22MEETYOUR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A54%2C%22y%22%3A219%2C%22width%22%3A482%2C%22height%22%3A60%2C%22text%22%3A%22THINKING%20PARTNER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A57%2C%22y%22%3A304%2C%22width%22%3A489%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22TACKLE%20ANY%20BIG%2CBOLD%2C%20BEWILDERING%20CHALLENGE%20WITH%20CLAUDE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A391%2C%22y%22%3A384%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22ASK%20CLAUDE%20%E4%B8%AA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A74%2C%22y%22%3A385%2C%22width%22%3A176%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22HOW%20CAN%20I%20HELP%20YOU%20TODAY%3F%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A81%2C%22y%22%3A437%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22WRITE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A223%2C%22y%22%3A437%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22%2F%3E%20%20CODE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A161%2C%22y%22%3A438%2C%22width%22%3A32%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22LEARN%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23eeece7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud6e8fc52%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0424089b\" id=\"u0424089b\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u74489f3c\" id=\"u74489f3c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片来自克劳德网站</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2ba7f447\" id=\"u2ba7f447\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0db2a4a4\" id=\"u0db2a4a4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但与Perplexity的这段经历让我意识到了一些我一直注意到却未曾真正意识到的事情：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6020941a\" id=\"u6020941a\"><strong><em><span data-lake-id=\"u150b032b\" id=\"u150b032b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">2020 年到 2025 年间，发生了一些微妙但深刻的变化：科技——尤其是人工智能——不再试图展现未来的样子。</span></em></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6b63658b\" id=\"u6b63658b\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue1a63e67\" id=\"ue1a63e67\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">当当今最强大的技术选择看起来</span></strong><strong><em><span data-lake-id=\"u65a2af46\" id=\"u65a2af46\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">不那么</span></em></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u31794c73\" id=\"u31794c73\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">强大时，这意味着什么？</span></strong></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"bfSGL\" id=\"bfSGL\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4b0624ce\" id=\"u4b0624ce\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">理解模式</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u2ed617d9\" id=\"u2ed617d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u038e98d7\" id=\"u038e98d7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但要理解这种转变为何重要，我们需要了解设计究竟起到了什么作用。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uda97735a\" id=\"uda97735a\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub8ed51af\" id=\"ub8ed51af\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计不仅仅是描述产品，它还提出了各种关系。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9575e0f7\" id=\"u9575e0f7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">它塑造了我们对技术的理解、我们与技术的互动方式，以及我们允许技术在我们的生活中扮演的角色。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u05369b5f\" id=\"u05369b5f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf3810f5b\" id=\"uf3810f5b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">贯穿这些关系的是一条情感线索。过去二十年来，技术设计经历了从</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5a1bd5e0\" id=\"u5a1bd5e0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">乐观→愤世嫉俗→同理心的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf9919f06\" id=\"uf9919f06\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">转变——这不仅反映了我们希望技术实现的功能，也反映了我们对技术未来可能性的感受。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucfdc1db3\" id=\"ucfdc1db3\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4b8224c6\" id=\"u4b8224c6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">每个时代都反映了我们共同协商建立的关系和情感。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u254bf6fc\" id=\"u254bf6fc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u420c3420\" id=\"u420c3420\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">它们通过协商而产生：公司做出设计选择，消费者对感觉对或错做出反应，文化时刻创造对某些关系的渴望，而我们的集体意识塑造了接下来要建造的东西。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf7723d56\" id=\"uf7723d56\"><span data-lake-id=\"u753e6546\" id=\"u753e6546\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">为了了解这种关系是如何演变的，让我们回顾一下我们与科技关系的三个时代。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"M3e1E\" id=\"M3e1E\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6f5765a8\" id=\"u6f5765a8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">第一时期：颠覆者（2010–2020）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u0e92006a\" id=\"u0e92006a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u08a4d2af\" id=\"u08a4d2af\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">关系</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub8054334\" id=\"ub8054334\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8a5fcb62\" id=\"u8a5fcb62\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">科技作为对现有体制的挑战者</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"nKIvj\" id=\"nKIvj\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u45860a39\" id=\"u45860a39\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">情绪</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u624e0335\" id=\"u624e0335\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：乐观</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u3a940016\" id=\"u3a940016\"><span data-lake-id=\"u070a7398\" id=\"u070a7398\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">2008年的金融危机让我们</span><a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/leadership/how-purple-uber-and-airbnb-are-disrupting-and-redefining/273650\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u9ac994d0\" id=\"u9ac994d0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u16f34765\" id=\"u16f34765\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">对传统机构</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u2e4d56ee\" id=\"u2e4d56ee\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">——银行、出租车垄断企业、连锁酒店，甚至本应保护我们的市场——都产生了深深的不信任感。与此同时，智能手机革命开启了新的可能性。突然间，所有沿用了几十年的模式都显得过时，亟待被取代。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8b459819\" id=\"u8b459819\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0c51af05\" id=\"u0c51af05\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这催生了一种特定的需求：我们希望科技能够挑战那些曾经让我们失望的体系。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uce22507e\" id=\"uce22507e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">那是一个充满乐观的时代</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc54cbacd\" id=\"uc54cbacd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">——我们相信科技可以修复破碎的系统。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"dp773\" id=\"dp773\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucaf92e22\" id=\"ucaf92e22\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">公司如何应对</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc4f7f3e0\" id=\"uc4f7f3e0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8ea14de0\" id=\"u8ea14de0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">他们以大胆的言辞来定位自己：</span></p><ul list=\"uf42e314e\"><li fid=\"u3fbdb296\" data-lake-id=\"u48e14f0c\" id=\"u48e14f0c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u683be4e5\" id=\"u683be4e5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Uber承诺“</span><a href=\"https://www.comparably.com/companies/uber/mission\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u85692b5b\" id=\"u85692b5b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fcfe4ec\" id=\"u7fcfe4ec\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">重新构想世界的出行方式</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"ub67b599f\" id=\"ub67b599f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">”。</span></li><li fid=\"u3fbdb296\" data-lake-id=\"u9b36a5ef\" id=\"u9b36a5ef\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucd51fe7d\" id=\"ucd51fe7d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Stripe宣称其使命是“</span><a href=\"https://www.comparably.com/companies/stripe/mission\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u0491cbf7\" id=\"u0491cbf7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3e68eb2e\" id=\"u3e68eb2e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">提高互联网的GDP</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"ud87426e0\" id=\"ud87426e0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u51d4103e\" id=\"u51d4103e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">”。</span></li><li fid=\"u3fbdb296\" data-lake-id=\"u3df47436\" id=\"u3df47436\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueb85e9ec\" id=\"ueb85e9ec\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Netflix的目标是“</span><a href=\"https://about.netflix.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u24d76a94\" id=\"u24d76a94\"><span data-lake-id=\"udc658add\" id=\"udc658add\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">娱乐全世界</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u4504bd1e\" id=\"u4504bd1e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">”。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u884f8580\" id=\"u884f8580\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3a2d82c\" id=\"ud3a2d82c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些不仅仅是宣传口号，更是对合作关系的提议：“让我们代表你挑战旧秩序。”</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"QryaT\" id=\"QryaT\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u76444a17\" id=\"u76444a17\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这在设计中是如何体现的？</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u90062c4d\" id=\"u90062c4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0afab92a\" id=\"u0afab92a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计成为这种自信的视觉体现，其特点是大胆的色彩、几何的精确性和极简的清晰度，反映了其使命的雄心壮志。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1c4ea4ff\" id=\"u1c4ea4ff\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3ca3df01\" id=\"u3ca3df01\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u99154598\" id=\"u99154598\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176676853-2c01e74b-aef2-406e-8528-c2ff2eca1cc6.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5414804d-0426-4a35-a927-e7e841e26e4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A395%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A660696%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A789%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22N%20BOLD%20DESIGN%20MINIMALISM%20COLORS%20REFLECTED%20BOLD%20NEW%20CONFIDENCE%20GEOMETRIC%20SHAPES%20%E4%B8%AA%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A383%2C%22y%22%3A113%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A172%2C%22text%22%3A%22N%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A91%2C%22y%22%3A157%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22BOLD%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A973%2C%22y%22%3A173%2C%22width%22%3A219%2C%22height%22%3A70%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A637%2C%22y%22%3A184%2C%22width%22%3A185%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22MINIMALISM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A92%2C%22y%22%3A217%2C%22width%22%3A104%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22COLORS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A971%2C%22y%22%3A251%2C%22width%22%3A278%2C%22height%22%3A59%2C%22text%22%3A%22REFLECTED%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A974%2C%22y%22%3A331%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A51%2C%22text%22%3A%22BOLD%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1130%2C%22y%22%3A342%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A41%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEW%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A972%2C%22y%22%3A407%2C%22width%22%3A342%2C%22height%22%3A57%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONFIDENCE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A346%2C%22y%22%3A549%2C%22width%22%3A171%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22GEOMETRIC%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A345%2C%22y%22%3A606%2C%22width%22%3A123%2C%22height%22%3A40%2C%22text%22%3A%22SHAPES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1268%2C%22y%22%3A674%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A72%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%AA%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23a0eac4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u982a9e49%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf6d2f638\" id=\"uf6d2f638\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u044c37f1\" id=\"u044c37f1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片来源于网络和官方产品网站；拼贴画由作者创作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub1f1deac\" id=\"ub1f1deac\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub42f6c31\" id=\"ub42f6c31\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">令我印象深刻的是，设计如何成为了乐观主义的视觉体现。设计语言传递着这样的信息：“我们充满自信。我们与众不同。我们在这里为你而战。”我们接受了这一理念。我们下载了这些应用。我们改变了自己的行为。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u639b429d\" id=\"u639b429d\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u24139a98\" id=\"u24139a98\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">携手合作：企业提供服务，消费者接受服务。我们建立了一种以技术为挑战者的合作关系。</span></em></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"B2evM\" id=\"B2evM\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue1abc380\" id=\"ue1abc380\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">第二阶段：激进派——去中心化（2015–2021）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u0586884a\" id=\"u0586884a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub5bc37e3\" id=\"ub5bc37e3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">关系：技术作为人类系统的替代品</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"TYRIs\" id=\"TYRIs\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a19b759\" id=\"u6a19b759\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">情绪：愤世嫉俗</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u61618fa8\" id=\"u61618fa8\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufdb4a93e\" id=\"ufdb4a93e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但乐观情绪并未持续太久。一股更为阴暗的情绪正在酝酿。</span><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/the-nsa-files\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u9b9bdecd\" id=\"u9b9bdecd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c8503c8\" id=\"u8c8503c8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">斯诺登的爆料</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u9ea7ddd1\" id=\"u9ea7ddd1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">和</span><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/news/2018/mar/17/cambridge-analytica-facebook-influence-us-election\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u4abb7e25\" id=\"u4abb7e25\"><span data-lake-id=\"u109a033e\" id=\"u109a033e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">剑桥分析公司</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u27951445\" id=\"u27951445\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">事件之后，一种新的结论开始传播：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u35b1bdee\" id=\"u35b1bdee\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">问题不仅仅在于制度的弊端，更在于人本身。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3294e497\" id=\"u3294e497\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8fbbecfb\" id=\"u8fbbecfb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">腐败。偏见。低效。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u730a592d\" id=\"u730a592d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2611cc20\" id=\"u2611cc20\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这是一种愤世嫉俗的转变：如果问题出在人类身上呢？或许我们需要用技术彻底取代人类的控制。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf231a8e8\" id=\"uf231a8e8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">一种新的信念应运而生：</span></strong><a href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/blockchain/articles/10.3389/fbloc.2023.1109544/full\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ud5247ca7\" id=\"ud5247ca7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1bb1617a\" id=\"u1bb1617a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">“代码即法律”。</span></strong></a><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uab882054\" id=\"uab882054\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">相信算法，而非人。</span></strong></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"eSIKy\" id=\"eSIKy\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufa72b4e4\" id=\"ufa72b4e4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这在设计中是如何体现的？</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ude8e8fe9\" id=\"ude8e8fe9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8a896870\" id=\"u8a896870\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">如果说颠覆是大胆的，那么去中心化就是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3027c82b\" id=\"u3027c82b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">极致的。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua37c8600\" id=\"ua37c8600\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c6700ff\" id=\"u1c6700ff\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我见过很多加密货币产品采用深色模式，搭配色彩鲜艳、近乎迷幻的配色。我还见过一些加密货币产品使用宇宙意象、霓虹渐变色，以及极致的视觉冲击力。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u398ebf35\" id=\"u398ebf35\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这些设计仿佛在低语：“我们来自未来。我们超越了人类的局限。”</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8c0345a1\" id=\"u8c0345a1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud47f5bc7\" id=\"ud47f5bc7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">加密货币领域人士都知道的两款产品：</span></p><ul list=\"ua6347453\"><li fid=\"uc6a35ddb\" data-lake-id=\"u85a25c00\" id=\"u85a25c00\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6da98501\" id=\"u6da98501\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">以太坊</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u50be0e1b\" id=\"u50be0e1b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">——一幅充满乌托邦色彩的插画，人们聚集在以紫色到青色渐变渲染的几何菱形标志周围。我非常喜欢</span><a href=\"https://liamcobb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"uadf8061a\" id=\"uadf8061a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27db62a8\" id=\"u27db62a8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">利亚姆·科布</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"uca5ab082\" id=\"uca5ab082\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">为以太坊创作的复古未来主义艺术作品。</span></li><li fid=\"uc6a35ddb\" data-lake-id=\"u19f93a4b\" id=\"u19f93a4b\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u950fdc18\" id=\"u950fdc18\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">OpenSea——</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue98bd1c8\" id=\"ue98bd1c8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">现代设计，绚丽的彩虹渐变色，颂扬数字艺术</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u69377277\" id=\"u69377277\"><span data-lake-id=\"u095297e7\" id=\"u095297e7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8b264a1e\" id=\"u8b264a1e\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176677361-c5dc1e11-1242-4b3c-bcb3-a4986f9974b6.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u451d7128-7ba5-4d28-96a1-d490627b129%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A394%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A1085564%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A788%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22Q%2C%20SEARCH%20OPENSEA%20%26A%20LANGUAGES%20EN%20LEAMUSE%20ALL%20PODGY%20PENGUINS%20UI%20PODGYS%20BYWASSIES%20FLOOR%20PRICE%20WELCOME%20TO%20ETHEREUM%20FEATURED%20COLLECTIONS%20CHECKS-VVORIGINALS%20%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%20ANEW%20WAY%20CRYPTO%20WITHOUT%20VOLATILITY%20MUTANT%20APE%20YACHT%20CLUB%20SUPEKS%20TO%20USE%20THE%20QUINE%20BY%20LARVA%20LABR%20INTERNET%20A%20FAIRER%20FINANCIAL%20SYSTEM%20BITLONS%20CAN'T%20APEN%20BANK%20ACCOUNTS%20OR%20FREELY%20USE%20THEIR%20MONEY.%20ETHEREUM'S%20FINANCLAL%20SYSTEM%20IS%20ALWAYS%20OPEN%20AND%20MAXIMALIST%20AND%20INNOVATIVE%20APPS%20EMEREUM%20APPS%20WORK%20WITHOUT%20SELLING%20YOUR%20FUTURISTIC%20DESIGN%20THE%20NETWORK%20OF%20NETWORKS%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A737%2C%22y%22%3A60%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22Q%2C%20SEARCH%20OPENSEA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A569%2C%22y%22%3A64%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22%26A%20LANGUAGES%20EN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A83%2C%22y%22%3A64%2C%22width%22%3A57%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22LEAMUSE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A970%2C%22y%22%3A98%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1269%2C%22y%22%3A148%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22PODGY%20PENGUINS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1271%2C%22y%22%3A223%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A10%2C%22text%22%3A%22UI%20PODGYS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A741%2C%22y%22%3A261%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22BYWASSIES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A752%2C%22y%22%3A307%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A10%2C%22text%22%3A%22FLOOR%20PRICE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A229%2C%22y%22%3A331%2C%22width%22%3A232%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22WELCOME%20TO%20ETHEREUM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A731%2C%22y%22%3A379%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22FEATURED%20COLLECTIONS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1269%2C%22y%22%3A405%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHECKS-VVORIGINALS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A764%2C%22y%22%3A415%2C%22width%22%3A12%2C%22height%22%3A61%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A425%2C%22width%22%3A149%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22ANEW%20WAY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A393%2C%22y%22%3A428%2C%22width%22%3A161%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22CRYPTO%20WITHOUT%20VOLATILITY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1269%2C%22y%22%3A442%2C%22width%22%3A83%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22MUTANT%20APE%20YACHT%20CLUB%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1026%2C%22y%22%3A442%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22SUPEKS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A454%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22TO%20USE%20THE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1268%2C%22y%22%3A478%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22QUINE%20BY%20LARVA%20LABR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A64%2C%22y%22%3A486%2C%22width%22%3A112%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22INTERNET%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A79%2C%22y%22%3A543%2C%22width%22%3A161%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22A%20FAIRER%20FINANCIAL%20SYSTEM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A76%2C%22y%22%3A562%2C%22width%22%3A177%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22BITLONS%20CAN'T%20APEN%20BANK%20ACCOUNTS%20OR%20FREELY%20USE%20THEIR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A76%2C%22y%22%3A573%2C%22width%22%3A189%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22MONEY.%20ETHEREUM'S%20FINANCLAL%20SYSTEM%20IS%20ALWAYS%20OPEN%20AND%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A702%2C%22y%22%3A580%2C%22width%22%3A407%2C%22height%22%3A49%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAXIMALIST%20AND%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A473%2C%22y%22%3A583%2C%22width%22%3A107%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22INNOVATIVE%20APPS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A472%2C%22y%22%3A601%2C%22width%22%3A138%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22EMEREUM%20APPS%20WORK%20WITHOUT%20SELLING%20YOUR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A699%2C%22y%22%3A639%2C%22width%22%3A432%2C%22height%22%3A61%2C%22text%22%3A%22FUTURISTIC%20DESIGN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A304%2C%22y%22%3A698%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20NETWORK%20OF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A305%2C%22y%22%3A717%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22NETWORKS%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23d1e2e9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u9ecb81a3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u49e2a55d\" id=\"u49e2a55d\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c422564\" id=\"u3c422564\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片来源于官方产品网站；拼贴画由作者创作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2721c156\" id=\"u2721c156\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubb11bb2e\" id=\"ubb11bb2e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">并非所有人都接受这一提议，因此这种合作关系始终局限于小众领域。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7308a742\" id=\"u7308a742\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但曾几何时，它代表了“科技解决一切”理念的极致延伸。这是科技极端主义的巅峰之作——与任何传统或人为控制的事物都背道而驰。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7f985705\" id=\"u7f985705\"><span data-lake-id=\"u66817cdb\" id=\"u66817cdb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">当时的文化环境允许了这一点。设计表达了这一点。有些人相信这一点。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u64d97a8a\" id=\"u64d97a8a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8b5840d\" id=\"ub8b5840d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但某种变化即将发生……</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"CLPs3\" id=\"CLPs3\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf071c926\" id=\"uf071c926\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">第三阶段：转折点——人工智能（2020-2025）</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u5ff6bc0a\" id=\"u5ff6bc0a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u714e4f72\" id=\"u714e4f72\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">关系：科技作为人类的伙伴</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"eWqEI\" id=\"eWqEI\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u25fb0530\" id=\"u25fb0530\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">情感：同理心</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u7c92869b\" id=\"u7c92869b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3dbb0821\" id=\"u3dbb0821\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">犬儒主义达到了顶峰。接下来出现的是一种更为温和的东西：同理心。然后人工智能出现了——一切都改变了。因为人工智能跨越了以往任何技术都未曾跨越的界限。它更强大，更具颠覆性，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3b0babb6\" id=\"u3b0babb6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">也更具根本性的威胁。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9e3064a2\" id=\"u9e3064a2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue28973e4\" id=\"ue28973e4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">应用程序颠覆了出租车行业。加密货币曾承诺取代银行。但人工智能呢？</span><a href=\"https://news.microsoft.com/source/features/ai/6-ai-trends-youll-see-more-of-in-2025/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u47043f8f\" id=\"u47043f8f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc9799bc4\" id=\"uc9799bc4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">人工智能可以思考、写作、创造和推理</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u2203b49c\" id=\"u2203b49c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。它正在闯入我们一直以来认为只有人类才能掌握的领域。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucdd4f3bb\" id=\"ucdd4f3bb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">早期的技术颠覆了我们的工作方式，而人工智能则颠覆了我们是谁。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u51d1c28f\" id=\"u51d1c28f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc7f7850f\" id=\"uc7f7850f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">关键区别在于：</span><a href=\"https://spectrum.ieee.org/what-is-the-uncanny-valley\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u3f035546\" id=\"u3f035546\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc805fe04\" id=\"uc805fe04\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">人工智能引发了“恐怖谷效应</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u617a8ffc\" id=\"u617a8ffc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">”。当某种事物看起来“几乎像人”时，我们的情绪反应会骤然变得不适。这种文化焦虑要求建立一种不同的关系，一种充满同理心的关系。理念也随之转变：</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u48975ea4\" id=\"u48975ea4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">技术应该帮助人类，而不是取代人类。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u540f2c34\" id=\"u540f2c34\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u917c6141\" id=\"u917c6141\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">这种矛盾造成了一个悖论——有史以来最强大的技术却不能看起来很强大。</span></strong></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"wSXj3\" id=\"wSXj3\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua43431b9\" id=\"ua43431b9\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">公司如何应对</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ub1b70705\" id=\"ub1b70705\"><span data-lake-id=\"u11c4057a\" id=\"u11c4057a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">于是各公司提出了合作方案。</span><a href=\"https://copilot.microsoft.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u8b0dbe51\" id=\"u8b0dbe51\"><span data-lake-id=\"u55261bff\" id=\"u55261bff\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">微软将其人工智能产品命名为“Copilot”，</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"uce4cf30e\" id=\"uce4cf30e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">标语是</span><a href=\"https://copilot.microsoft.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ub5260fe6\" id=\"ub5260fe6\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf008412d\" id=\"uf008412d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">“你的信息、娱乐和灵感伙伴”；</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u9124f838\" id=\"u9124f838\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"ucd82f7ae\" id=\"ucd82f7ae\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Claude 定位为“你的人工智能助手”；ChatGPT 则选择了对话式的“聊天”而非技术性的框架。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"suJrg\" id=\"suJrg\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u935cfe0f\" id=\"u935cfe0f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这在设计中是如何体现的？</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ufef188af\" id=\"ufef188af\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8128cae1\" id=\"u8128cae1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计语言刻意柔化，以表达这种富有同理心的合作关系。</span></p><ul list=\"u426df71e\"><li fid=\"u0b806440\" data-lake-id=\"uaa27f054\" id=\"uaa27f054\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u162aae02\" id=\"u162aae02\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Claude</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u68763576\" id=\"u68763576\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">的暖橙色和柔和的字体给人以人性化的感觉，而不是高科技感。</span></li><li fid=\"u0b806440\" data-lake-id=\"u81ad1fdc\" id=\"u81ad1fdc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6a74b658\" id=\"u6a74b658\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Cursor</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u42647287\" id=\"u42647287\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">是一款 AI 原生代码编辑器，它采用宁静的背景和留白，更像是一款阅读应用，而不是一款开发工具。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u258de9ea\" id=\"u258de9ea\"><span data-lake-id=\"u080e7482\" id=\"u080e7482\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua9de7aa8\" id=\"ua9de7aa8\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176678240-bb5c1f93-3c1f-4a31-a213-c74e56b49308.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u69c105f1-727d-4325-8a31-247b3244dd4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A394%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A611653%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A788%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22OCURSON%20BUILD%20WITH%20CLAUDE%20START%20DEVELOPING%20CLAUDEPOWERED%20APPLICATIONS%20WITH%20OUR%20BUILT%20TO%20MAKE%20YOU%20EXTRAORDINARILY%20PRODUCTIVE.%20COMPREHENSIVE%20API%20GUIDES%20AND%20BEST%20PRACTICES%20CURSOR%20IS%20THE%20BEST%20WAY%20TO%20CODE%20WITH%20AL%20CLAUDE%20FOR%20WORK%20LEARN%20TO%20IMPLEMENT%20CLAUDE%20ACROSS%20YOURORGANIZATION%20SER%20ANTE%20TOR%20AN%20DOR%20ANE%20REAR%20ANDE%20ROARE%20SEAR%20ANE%20SEN%20THER%20O%20SO%20SAS%20TERETTERTTER%20WAWT-LIN%20NOER%20WIST%20N%20SEN%20CLAUDE%20FOR%20PERSONAL%20TREIAG%3A%20MP%2C%20TREDE%2FVEL%20ESLIT.%20CENTHE%20SEMENLE%20TRANSTANE%2CTIET%60TERANSFARNS%20DISCOVER%20HOW%20TO%20LEVERAGE%20CLAUDE'S%20CAPABILITIES%20FOR%20YOUR%2072MI%20CALM%20TECHNOLOGY%20TANE%20TO%20USHERYT%20ENERYT%20CONTHER%20AITH%20A%20REPORT%20HELDER%20THAT%20CONBINES%20A%20HUMAN-AL%20PROGRAMMER%2CORDERS%20OF%20WITH%20HUMAN%20WARMTH%20MAGNITUDE%20MORE%20EFFECTIVE%20THAN%20ANY%20IN%20ADI%20LEWS%20TO%20BET%20IN%20THE%20BELARLOUR%20VING%20A%20REPRESTE%20SUNPLE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A72%2C%22y%22%3A75%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22OCURSON%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A745%2C%22y%22%3A99%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22BUILD%20WITH%20CLAUDE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A744%2C%22y%22%3A126%2C%22width%22%3A239%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22START%20DEVELOPING%20CLAUDEPOWERED%20APPLICATIONS%20WITH%20OUR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A71%2C%22y%22%3A140%2C%22width%22%3A213%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22BUILT%20TO%20MAKE%20YOU%20EXTRAORDINARILY%20PRODUCTIVE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A744%2C%22y%22%3A141%2C%22width%22%3A212%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMPREHENSIVE%20API%20GUIDES%20AND%20BEST%20PRACTICES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A71%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A187%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22CURSOR%20IS%20THE%20BEST%20WAY%20TO%20CODE%20WITH%20AL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A751%2C%22y%22%3A262%2C%22width%22%3A139%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE%20FOR%20WORK%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A745%2C%22y%22%3A290%2C%22width%22%3A230%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22LEARN%20TO%20IMPLEMENT%20CLAUDE%20ACROSS%20YOURORGANIZATION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A384%2C%22y%22%3A307%2C%22width%22%3A161%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22SER%20ANTE%20TOR%20AN%20DOR%20ANE%20REAR%20ANDE%20ROARE%20SEAR%20ANE%20SEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A378%2C%22y%22%3A366%2C%22width%22%3A191%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22THER%20O%20SO%20SAS%20TERETTERTTER%20WAWT-LIN%20NOER%20WIST%20N%20SEN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A750%2C%22y%22%3A431%2C%22width%22%3A166%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE%20FOR%20PERSONAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A416%2C%22y%22%3A431%2C%22width%22%3A153%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22TREIAG%3A%20MP%2C%20TREDE%2FVEL%20ESLIT.%20CENTHE%20SEMENLE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A239%2C%22y%22%3A446%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22TRANSTANE%2CTIET%60TERANSFARNS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A748%2C%22y%22%3A458%2C%22width%22%3A232%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22DISCOVER%20HOW%20TO%20LEVERAGE%20CLAUDE'S%20CAPABILITIES%20FOR%20YOUR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1233%2C%22y%22%3A492%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%2272MI%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A708%2C%22y%22%3A590%2C%22width%22%3A444%2C%22height%22%3A62%2C%22text%22%3A%22CALM%20TECHNOLOGY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A386%2C%22y%22%3A649%2C%22width%22%3A177%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22TANE%20TO%20USHERYT%20ENERYT%20CONTHER%20AITH%20A%20REPORT%20HELDER%20THAT%20CONBINES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A76%2C%22y%22%3A653%2C%22width%22%3A142%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22A%20HUMAN-AL%20PROGRAMMER%2CORDERS%20OF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A706%2C%22y%22%3A658%2C%22width%22%3A514%2C%22height%22%3A46%2C%22text%22%3A%22WITH%20HUMAN%20WARMTH%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A75%2C%22y%22%3A665%2C%22width%22%3A149%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAGNITUDE%20MORE%20EFFECTIVE%20THAN%20ANY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A386%2C%22y%22%3A688%2C%22width%22%3A174%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22IN%20ADI%20LEWS%20TO%20BET%20IN%20THE%20BELARLOUR%20VING%20A%20REPRESTE%20SUNPLE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f1f1ee%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6ad936fe%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaaf2e91c\" id=\"uaaf2e91c\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u24c2af04\" id=\"u24c2af04\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片来源于官方产品网站；拼贴画由作者创作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u42424e88\" id=\"u42424e88\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uda1d8bf5\" id=\"uda1d8bf5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Perplexity Comet 的</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue00cf079\" id=\"ue00cf079\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计宗旨是精准——一个旨在提供清晰、可靠答案的搜索引擎。然而，它的渐变柔和，动态流畅，语调近乎温柔。它是有生命力的数据。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub2f213de\" id=\"ub2f213de\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8f3bb3f2\" id=\"u8f3bb3f2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">如果您有兴趣了解如何使用 Comet，</span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/8yY_tOqwDZE\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ud55c1247\" id=\"ud55c1247\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u25c02be1\" id=\"u25c02be1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: inherit\">我制作了一个视频，在四个真实场景中测试了 Comet——例如，在一个用例中，它通过一次提示订购了狗粮（令人印象深刻），但在另一个用例中，它却四次错位（不太令人印象深刻）。</span></strong></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud9919853\" id=\"ud9919853\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3951ca3f\" id=\"u3951ca3f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计开始提出这样的理念：“我与你同在，而非凌驾于你之上。”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub8fda089\" id=\"ub8fda089\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">技术不再被视为解决方案，而是辅助工具——是站在我们身边的助手，而不是取代我们的英雄。而我们也正在做出回应。我们正在尝试这种关系。使用这些工具。看看“伙伴”这种关系是否合适。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uef76644d\" id=\"uef76644d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u70c12a54\" id=\"u70c12a54\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">谈判正在实时进行——公司展现热情，用户决定是否信任，文化方面则密切关注合作框架是否站得住脚。</span></strong></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"XMMqn\" id=\"XMMqn\"><span data-lake-id=\"u422ba07b\" id=\"u422ba07b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">软革命</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uaf857f34\" id=\"uaf857f34\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8ba832fd\" id=\"u8ba832fd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">三种关系。三种情绪。从乐观地认为技术可以修复破碎的系统，到愤世嫉俗地认为人类才是问题所在，再到同理心——认识到最强大的技术必须与我们合作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue8bcddfb\" id=\"ue8bcddfb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u41059745\" id=\"u41059745\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\">按回车键或点击查看完整尺寸的图片</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u31efcd4d\" id=\"u31efcd4d\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1762176681556-f02a7bac-9415-4fb2-bad0-c9b4129c6ebd.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2a0b7d08-8c46-4bd3-9a59-a05a8c066ae%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ufe62dc6e-fe1e-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A467%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A3391297%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A933%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22THE%20SOFT%20REVOLUTION%3A%20THREE%20ERAS%2CTHREE%20RELATIONSHIPS%20YEARS%20RELATIONSHIP%20EMOTION%20ERA%20TECHNOLOGY%20OPTIMISM%202010-2020%20DISRUPTORS%20CHALLENGER%20AS%20TECHNOLOGY%20AS%20RADICAL%20CYNICISM%202015-2021%20REPLACEMENT%20WING%20MAXIMALIST%2C%20SOFT%2CWARM%2C%202020-2025%20AI%20ERA%20NEON%20GRADIENTS%20CONVERSATIONAL%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A283%2C%22y%22%3A52%2C%22width%22%3A771%2C%22height%22%3A62%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20SOFT%20REVOLUTION%3A%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A103%2C%22y%22%3A131%2C%22width%22%3A1147%2C%22height%22%3A63%2C%22text%22%3A%22THREE%20ERAS%2CTHREE%20RELATIONSHIPS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A343%2C%22y%22%3A255%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22YEARS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A581%2C%22y%22%3A255%2C%22width%22%3A294%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22RELATIONSHIP%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1010%2C%22y%22%3A256%2C%22width%22%3A189%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22EMOTION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A132%2C%22y%22%3A256%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22ERA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A614%2C%22y%22%3A355%2C%22width%22%3A211%2C%22height%22%3A49%2C%22text%22%3A%22TECHNOLOGY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1011%2C%22y%22%3A373%2C%22width%22%3A200%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22OPTIMISM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A318%2C%22y%22%3A377%2C%22width%22%3A198%2C%22height%22%3A38%2C%22text%22%3A%222010-2020%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A66%2C%22y%22%3A380%2C%22width%22%3A200%2C%22height%22%3A38%2C%22text%22%3A%22DISRUPTORS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A633%2C%22y%22%3A406%2C%22width%22%3A209%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHALLENGER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A585%2C%22y%22%3A416%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22AS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A607%2C%22y%22%3A514%2C%22width%22%3A266%2C%22height%22%3A50%2C%22text%22%3A%22TECHNOLOGY%20AS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A91%2C%22y%22%3A521%2C%22width%22%3A151%2C%22height%22%3A41%2C%22text%22%3A%22RADICAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1012%2C%22y%22%3A538%2C%22width%22%3A186%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22CYNICISM%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A320%2C%22y%22%3A540%2C%22width%22%3A190%2C%22height%22%3A40%2C%22text%22%3A%222015-2021%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A607%2C%22y%22%3A568%2C%22width%22%3A245%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22REPLACEMENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A109%2C%22y%22%3A571%2C%22width%22%3A107%2C%22height%22%3A45%2C%22text%22%3A%22WING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A607%2C%22y%22%3A677%2C%22width%22%3A213%2C%22height%22%3A41%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAXIMALIST%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1007%2C%22y%22%3A679%2C%22width%22%3A220%2C%22height%22%3A40%2C%22text%22%3A%22SOFT%2CWARM%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A320%2C%22y%22%3A704%2C%22width%22%3A197%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%222020-2025%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A106%2C%22y%22%3A706%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A39%2C%22text%22%3A%22AI%20ERA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A573%2C%22y%22%3A729%2C%22width%22%3A292%2C%22height%22%3A42%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEON%20GRADIENTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A962%2C%22y%22%3A730%2C%22width%22%3A282%2C%22height%22%3A39%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONVERSATIONAL%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e3d9c9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u090f46a2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uac7019f0\" id=\"uac7019f0\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1d18d648\" id=\"u1d18d648\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">图片由 ChatGPT 生成——作者创意</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud8951b3e\" id=\"ud8951b3e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u42f783fb\" id=\"u42f783fb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">这种同理心的转变是真诚的吗？我们目前还不得而知。这可能是真正的进步，也可能是精心策划的品牌塑造。我们可能要过几年才能知道答案。</span></p><ul list=\"u7e25607d\"><li fid=\"u91c10c67\" data-lake-id=\"u7a88517a\" id=\"u7a88517a\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b52e14c\" id=\"u5b52e14c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">但我们确实知道：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u988c50e7\" id=\"u988c50e7\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计提出关系，而这些关系是协商的——公司提出方案，人们接受或拒绝，文化塑造了什么是正确的。</span></li><li fid=\"u91c10c67\" data-lake-id=\"u2d0913db\" id=\"u2d0913db\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5f9e6449\" id=\"u5f9e6449\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">看清这种模式能让我们掌握主动权。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u98328ff8\" id=\"u98328ff8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">我们最终建立的关系并非预先注定，而是在每一次点击、每一次产品选择、每一个我们决定“这感觉对了”或“这感觉错了”的静默时刻中不断协商形成的。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ua03cb24d\" id=\"ua03cb24d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7ae75405\" id=\"u7ae75405\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">当 Perplexity 将精准融入诗意之中时，他们做出了选择。现在，轮到我们做出选择。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u32b52fa3\" id=\"u32b52fa3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">设计是指南针——指向我们想要构建的未来。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0fa382ed\" id=\"u0fa382ed\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u871c2d94\" id=\"u871c2d94\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">​</span></strong><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0c52994c\" id=\"u0c52994c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u53899c7a\" id=\"u53899c7a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://medium.com/design-bootcamp/from-disruption-to-connection-why-ai-design-is-becoming-more-human-a6df2f0e41b6\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u5fd32296\" id=\"u5fd32296\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3d1b28c2\" id=\"u3d1b28c2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://medium.com/design-bootcamp/from-disruption-to-connection-why-ai-design-is-becoming-more-human-a6df2f0e41b6</span></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2ff03a29\" id=\"u2ff03a29\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6d5353ad\" id=\"u6d5353ad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">​</span></strong><br></p>"}
